Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just quit while you're behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get anything out of facing reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no way to change it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to just ignore it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and believe only what you want to believe in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that sound a lot easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be awesome if everyone's life could be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing great about the real world, is there? It's just dull and annoying as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one accepts that's the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just stuck with it because they can't deny it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who actually succeed in life... They just happen to be born
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the magic ticket called "talent."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you realize that, all you have left in life is despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wouldn't it be better if that kind of reality was wiped away?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's complete bullshit!{Reality isn't a game!}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be faced with the boring reality that boxes you in, no matter where you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, we don't need our world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better to let it be swallowed up and for mankind to turn into Shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what all those people who're scared to death really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's my duty to see that they get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your bullshit to yourself!{more like fridge logic amirite}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to disappear, then go ahead! But leave us out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brats like you are so damned naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get that you're all afraid and gotta act tough to cover it up, but geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you all this based on my own experience in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell {\i1}is{\i0} that thing?{third impact}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon...{2deep4u}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon the worlds will merge into one!{cry moar tears}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a huge collection of energy!{massive hunk or hunk of massive?}{2 da moon}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming down fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once everyone turns into Shadows, they'll still keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll just be oblivious to all the things around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's that different from the way things are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this'll make things much easier for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you are, your lifespan is about 80 years or so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it'd be easier if we all just became Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to hold back anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more pretending we don't see things.{something about a cave}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants anything like that!{something about plato}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! I'm going bear-serk over here!{something about an allegory}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything Adachi says is just nuts!{>mfw}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember what it was like when your Shadow came out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been enjoying life far more than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those things move on pure instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They go wild because you defy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?{at least that didn't last 30 seconds and then end up with shinji crushing kaoru}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to use this.{or was it kaworu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined the police so I could carry a real gun, and I thought it'd be fun, but honestly, that was a wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around me was such an idiot.{especially that adachi guy ;D.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't know when to quit, do ya?{but yea, asuka's name was romanized differently between the anime and manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want so badly that you'd put yourselves in harm's way?{some pussy. I'd put myself in harm's way for some pussy}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some innate sense of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you just wanted something to spice up your dull lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you any different from criminals who get their kicks from murder?{durr}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just loiter around Junes and play guessing games!{lolok}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how many people out there actually think about what's real, or what's right and wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to none, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namatame was the one behind those serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's real in everyone's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you managed to catch me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what do you think would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's view would shift...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, no one actually cares who the real killer is.
