Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! I just told you everything there is to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your stubborn ignorance that makes you kids so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have the balls to shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?{and yu will be reborn as the one}
