Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.48,interface,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(106,0)\fscx850\fscy850\alpha&H2F&\blur1\frz0.1303\c&HFFFFFF&\move(598,517,584,517,22,189)}It's pulling them together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the two worlds are going to collide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what creates the fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mankind's desires are my desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who shepherds humans to their true desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are the ones who tore down the wall between image and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I decided to expand this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You played your part well, stirring up the will of the masses into madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even that is coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mankind will soon become Shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:12:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and live on in the darkness of the fog, oblivious of their reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is part of the sea of unconsciousness that exists within human hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a hollow forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,born from bloated desire and false imagery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sayin' you're the one who created this nasty-ass world?!{nasty ass-world}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bestowed power onto those who could brave the hollow forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was I who made it possible for you to bring about this destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the power to enter the TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans choose to see only what they wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a world filled with desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viewed through a window, from which one sees what one wishes to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why those who got famous suddenly appeared on the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all in people's minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Midnight Channel we saw in Namatame's hospital room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't Namatame's true intentions at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came on because we were all thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This person must be the killer. He can't be forgiven."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may not have seen the exact same thing when we watched it by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more false images one yearns for,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more one stops yearning for reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the forest grows on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the expansion of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did we wish for that crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To hell with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kept fighting and fighting like morons to get where we're standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... That I did not foresee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to master your own Shadow that emerged to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and use its power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new and uncertain facet of mankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it worthy to put my trust in, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone will turn into Shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the world will begin anew in its true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let our world come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you defy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a single person accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human bonds are unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not worthy of your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were humans not the ones who departed from reality of their own volition, craving more false images?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality isn't so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they were there with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!{gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of your Social Links
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}created a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!{My nigga!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!{senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, it's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, truly!{senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One shot, one kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll leave the world in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have proven to me human potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mankind's desires are my desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If mankind so wishes, I will return at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, children of the new potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here. I'm done for anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shadows will finish me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to kill me in the first place, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stupid game's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live and face your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it works in our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro and his friends beat up the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They saved us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED song start}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:43.30,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Only cruel words flood the town at random{mujihi na kotoba dake ga detarame ni machi ni afureteru}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:52.68,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Never more will that sad voice flow by{never more setsunaku nagareteta koe}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:21:02.82,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Casual days bid their goodbyes{nanige nai nichijou ga sayonara wo tsuge}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too soon to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro, I don't want you to go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:08.85,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}We have lost our
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:12.95,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}irreplaceable days together{bokura no kakegae no nai hi ushinawareteta}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, I'm going to marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:19.61,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}The misty rain hides the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:23.55,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and steals our light{taiyou kakusu kirisame hikari wo ubai}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd welcome you with open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hands off while she's underage!{harem complete}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you promise you wouldn't cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:29.77,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I was worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:37.65,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}having lost everything I believed in{shinjiru mono nakushiteta boku wa nayami dakedo}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave your room as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as much a part of this family as Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:44.99,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}But I will never forget
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:50.03,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}the days I spent with everyone{wasurenai yo daiji na minna to sugoshita mainichi}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I'm going back home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:55.18,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Never more will I be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:22:00.21,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}alone in the darkness{never more kurai yami mo hitori janai sa}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to work bear-y hard to protect that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The train will be arriving momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For your safety, please stand behind the white line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:05.88,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I will find everything dear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:09.97,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}that I've lost{mitsuke dasu yo daiji na nakushita mono wo}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While boarding, please do so promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you better go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:15.92,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Never more, for I am sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:24.07,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}your voice will lead the way{never more kimi no koe ga kitto sou boku wo michibiku yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:28.90,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}But I will never forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:34.24,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}the days I spent with everyone{wasurenai yo daiji na minna to sugoshita mainichi}
