Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:12.66,ED,,0000,0010,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)\an9}I still remember{ima mo obeteru}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:18.96,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}The night...{Kimi ni...}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had quite the eventful journey for someone your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a crystal of power which you have nurtured through your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An orb that repels fabrications of all sorts, dispels lies, and shines upon the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have formed bonds with those dear to you as you reached out to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll continue to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go. You'd best be off.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:16.26,0:24:19.39,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fs70\fad(612,474)\fnCentury\b1\pos(658,242)\c&HF7FCFF&\t(\fsp2)}It is... a story of reality
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:19.39,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&HFF&\bord2\blur3\fs70\fad(612,474)\fnCentury\b1\pos(658,242)\c&HF7FCFF&\t(\fsp2)\3c&H101118&}It is... a story of reality
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a crystal of power which you have nurtured through your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.77,0:24:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't forget about me, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.27,0:24:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is an illusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as we're all together, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.69,0:24:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.99,0:24:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.86,0:24:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.61,0:24:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Someone, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.57,0:24:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.45,0:24:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate it all had to come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.12,0:24:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
